Developer Terms of Use
des: Hear what real people think about today's top stories by listening into actual conversations on the latest topics enacted in the virtual tea room of Teatime Chat. You can even ask the skill to discuss any topic on your mind and hear people chat about it over a cup of tea! Get started by starting the skill by asking Alexa to open Teatime chat and then asking for the topic of the day.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
